elocity on non-equilibrium parameter ($q-1$) is\ncharacterized by two second-order polynomials. Both $a$ and $d\\xi$ from the\npolynomials fit, related to the influence of the system bulk viscosity,\nincrease toward lower RHIC energies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 5 Dec 2020 09:31:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Sep 2021 04:03:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-03"}
